_sText:
This is my very first map.

I just learned how to map today so dont make fun of its low difficulty.

The point of this map is to plant the bomb in the middle of the map.  The surrounding structure has ladders leading up to it and can be used as a sniping spot.  The two bases, where you spawn, have stairs leading up to the top of them.  This is only the Alpha version so expect more versions to be released in the future.
